description:
Create lib/translate-order.ts function that takes order object from Supabase and generates Chinese-formatted text using template: '新订单 #{order_id}
产品: {tier} 级毛领
颜色: {color_zh}
尺寸: {size}
数量: 1
收货地址:
{transliterated_address}
'. Use OpenAI GPT-4 to transliterate English address to Chinese format (e.g., 'Vancouver BC' → '温哥华, 不列颠哥伦比亚省'). Cache OPENAI_API_KEY in .env.local. Export function for use in API routes. Add test cases for US, Canada, UK addresses.
